<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Impact Tuition Classes</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f5efe6;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --text: #1f2937;
            --muted: #607080;
            --accent: #d97706;
        }
        *{
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf2, var(--bg));
        }
        .wrap {
            width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 16px));
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 12px 0 20px;
        }
        .hero,
        .section,
        .box {
            background: var(--card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.08);
        }
        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
            gap: 14px;
            padding: 18px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding: 18px;
        }
        .section-title {
            margin: 10px 0 6px;
        }
        .right {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1f2937, #374151);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .photo {
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .photo img {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .photo p {
            padding: 12px 14px 14px;
        }
        .box {
            padding: 14px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.08);
            background: #fffdf8;
        }
        .right .box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        }
        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 7px 11px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.12);
            color: #b45309;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        h1,
        h2,
        h3,
        p,
        ul{
            margin: 0;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.7rem);
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 12px 0;
        }
        p {
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.65;
        }
        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 11px 16px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .primary {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .secondary {
            border: 1px solid #d7dce1;
            color: var(--text);
        }
        .stats,
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 14px;
        }
        .box strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        li {
            margin-left: 18px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: inherit;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 0 0;
            color: var(--muted);
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .hero,
            .stats,
            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 560px) {
            .wrap {
                width: min(100% - 12px, 1100px);
            }
            .hero,
            .section {
                padding: 14px;
            }
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="wrap">
        <section class="hero">
            <div>
                <span class="tag">Impact Tuition Classes</span>
                <h1>Learn better. Score higher.</h1>
                <p>Simple, focused tuition for school students with clear teaching, regular practice, and personal attention.</p>
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a class="btn primary" href="#programs">Programs</a>
                    <a class="btn secondary" href="#contact">Contact</a>
                </div>
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="box"><strong>12+</strong>Years</div>
                    <div class="box"><strong>500+</strong>Students</div>
                    <div class="box"><strong>1:10</strong>Batch size</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <aside class="right">
                <div class="box photo">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523240795612-9a054b0db644?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Students studying in a classroom">
                    <p>Focused learning in a calm classroom environment.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h2>Why choose us</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Concept-based teaching</li>
                        <li>Weekly tests and worksheets</li>
                        <li>Personal doubt clearing</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <h3>Subjects</h3>
                    <p>Math, Science, English, and exam preparation.</p>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </section>
        <section class="section" id="programs">
            <span class="tag">Programs</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Learning support for every stage</h2>
            <p>Primary tuition, secondary coaching, and test preparation in one simple layout.</p>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="box"><h3>Primary</h3><p>Basics, reading, writing, homework help.</p></div>
                <div class="box"><h3>Secondary</h3><p>Subject-wise classes and board exam support.</p></div>
                <div class="box"><h3>Tests</h3><p>Mock tests, revision, and doubt solving.</p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid" style="margin-top:10px;" id="contact">
                <div class="box"><h3>Schedule</h3><p>Mon to Fri classes with weekend revision.</p></div>
                <div class="box"><h3>Contact</h3><p>Call for admission on:9876543210</p></div>
                <div class="box"><h3>Focus</h3><p>Clear teaching with small batches and care.</p></div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <footer>Impact Tuition Classes | Learning with discipline, confidence, and care.</footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
